on gametest projectile context:
    add 2 to arrow knockback strength of event-entity
    set arrow pierce level of event-entity to 3

on gametest piglin barter mutable:
    add stick to barter drops

on gametest entity death:
    set drops to diamond

on gametest explode mutable:
    set explosion block yield to 0

on gametest explosion prime mutable:
    set explosion yield to 3

on gametest explosive entity context:
    set explosive yield of event-entity to 5

on gametest hanging break:
    set test name of entity hanging entity to "hanging entity"
    set test name of entity hanging remover to "hanging remover"

on gametest block fertilize:
    set test block above fertilized blocks to gold_block
